data.description: Welcome to your stunning 2-story home in a top-grade school district. This meticulously maintained 4-bed, 2-bath residence boasts high windows for abundant natural light, a remodeled master bath, and a half bath on the first floor perfect for entertaining guest. Upgraded with a newer 5-ton AC unit, hurricane category 5-rated windows, and accordion shutters on second floor. The fenced backyard includes a shed and cement slab. Enjoy community amenities like a heated pool, 3 parks, 7 lakes, pickle-ball, tennis, bike trails, and basketball courts. Basic internet included. HOA rules apply. Including no commercial vehicles and a one year lease restriction. Schedule a viewing today!
